# Runtime manifest

- Manifest format: JSON, `version: 1`, required `schema` → `libs/runtime-manifest/schemas/manifest/runtime.v1.schema.json` (`MANIFEST_SCHEMA_PATH`), `agents[]` with **`name` only**, optional `webhooks: [{ "source": "…" }]`, optional `pollers[]`, optional `adapters: [{ "source": "…" }]`.
- Agent **definitions** (`defineAgent`: `handles`, `usesAdapters`, `run`) live in agent packages and **`apps/worker/src/shipped-agents.ts`** — not in manifest JSON.
- Scenario files under `scenarios/**/*.scenarios.json` use `scenarioFileSchema`. Each scenario declares **`manifests[]`** (manifest `name` values). Adapter mocks on scenarios only — not on manifest agents.
- Default path: `manifests/application.json`. Override with `npm run dev -- --manifest <path>` or `SYNAPSE_RUNTIME_MANIFEST`.
- **`npm run dev`** loads the manifest (default `manifests/application.json`; override with `--manifest`), validates against `shippedAgents` + `knownEventTypes`, configures ingress, prints `synapse manifest: <abs path>`.
- **`npm run dev:once`** defaults to `manifests/application.json`; optional `--manifest` must match the worker `SYNAPSE_RUNTIME_MANIFEST`. Requires `npm run dev` running. Discovers scenarios whose `manifests[]` includes the manifest `name`.
- Webhook/poll catalog ids: `libs/runtime-manifest/src/webhook-route-catalog.ts`, `poll-source-catalog.ts`; routes in `apps/ingress`.
